# Assets and Themes Layout

- App-served themes: [`public/themes`](mdc:public/themes)
  - Example theme JSONs: [`public/themes/analogue-os-menu-es-de.json`](mdc:public/themes/analogue-os-menu-es-de.json), [`public/themes/atari-50-menu-es-de.json`](mdc:public/themes/atari-50-menu-es-de.json), [`public/themes/mania-menu-es-de.json`](mdc:public/themes/mania-menu-es-de.json)
  - Per-theme assets (fonts/images) under `public/themes/<theme>/_inc/...`
- Source themes and assets: [`es-de_themes`](mdc:es-de_themes)
- Emulator cores and WASM: [`public/cores`](mdc:public/cores)
- Frontend bundle assets: [`public/assets/frontend`](mdc:public/assets/frontend)

Notes:
- Keep file paths consistent between source and output to simplify lookups.